PrecisAmendment to the CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD REGULATIONS establishing a higher initial payment for the base grades of wheat (an increase of $12 from $112 to $124 per metric tonne) and amber durum wheat (an increase of $12 from $108 to $120 per metric tonne) for the 1992-93 crop year.
